Hello, how can i turn on Target ROAS campaign?

Hi Denys! To turn on a Target ROAS campaign, you'll need to follow these steps:
1. Ensure your Events meet the requirements: You need to have at least 20 complete_payment or sale events with event_value at the account level within the past 14 days.
2. Set your Campaign Objective to 'Website Conversions.'
3. Choose 'Conversion Value' as your Optimization Goal.
4. Select 'Target ROAS' as your Bid Type.
5. Set your ROAS goal in percentage.
For more detailed instructions, you can refer to this article: [Introduction to Target ROAS](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/31173203587085-Introduction-to-Target-ROAS). Let me know if you have any other questions!
